and departed for to go into Macedonia.","year":60},{"id":"recrngDzkoWscyHRq","ref":"Acts.20.2","text":"And when he had gone over those parts, and had given them much exhortation, he came into Greece,","year":60},{"id":"recsLjVb0FvkS7lJa","ref":"Acts.20.3","text":"And there abode three months. And when the Jews laid wait for him, as he was about to sail into Syria, he purposed to return through Macedonia.","year":60},{"id":"recnGeWHBsB7nkb5D","ref":"Acts.20.4","text":"And there accompanied him into Asia Sopater of Berea; and of the Thessalonians, Aristarchus and Secundus; and Gaius of Derbe, and Timotheus; and of Asia, Tychicus and Trophimus.","year":60},{"id":"recj9sV22qxWTUR1I","ref":"Acts.20.5","text":"These going before tarried for us at Troas.","year":60},{"id":"recXZTWnzQ7CSAEqY","ref":"Acts.20.6","text":"And we sailed away from Philippi after the days of unleavened bread, and came unto them to Troas in five days; where we abode seven days.","year":60},{"id":"recIYoA2baAwdPaY7","ref":"Acts.20.7","text":"And upon the first day of the week, when the disciples came together to break bread, Paul preached unto them, ready to depart on the morrow; and continued his speech until midnight.","year":60},{"id":"recldv7FccorBoaUA","ref":"Acts.20.8","text":"And there were many lights in the upper chamber, where they were gathered together.","year":60}]}
